NOTICE — Audio Assets

The files in assets/*/irs/ (*.irs), assets/*/presets/ (*.json), and
assets/*/source/ (*.xml) are derived from or identical to data distributed
by Lenovo Group Limited as part of the ThinkPad audio driver package
(n3ga127w.exe, driver ID DS557051). The Dolby DAX3 tuning data is
copyright Lenovo Group Limited and/or Dolby Laboratories. These files are
included here under the same rationale as binary firmware files distributed
by projects such as linux-firmware: they are vendor-supplied, unmodified
(source XML) or mechanically derived (IRS and JSON) hardware configuration
data necessary for correct hardware operation on Linux. No reverse
engineering of executable code was performed. All data was extracted from
the official, publicly available Lenovo driver package.

If you are Lenovo or Dolby and have concerns about this distribution, please
open an issue.
